# Payment Pages (SwiftPay Builder)

Module: `/payment-pages` and create-page wizard. Defines page shell, steps, and builder layout (not individual UI components).

## Dashboard (`/payment-pages`)
- Standard page pattern: `px-[32px] pt-[12px] pb-[32px] bg-white min-h-full`
- Action bar: "Create Page" Primary CTA (High emphasis, `Plus` icon) + search + filters
- Table: `grid-cols-[1.5fr_1.5fr_1fr_0.8fr_0.8fr_0.4fr]`, without vertical separators
- Status chips: Active `text-[#21c179] bg-[#e3f6ec]`, Expired `text-[#fd5154] bg-[#ffebef]`, Draft `text-[#7e7e7e] bg-[#fafafa]`
- Actions: kebab menu (Share, Download QR, Edit, Expire/Reactivate, Delete)

## Create Page Entry
- Popup (`type="form"`) with 4 option cards
- Each card: `border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-5 hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]`
- Icon: `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd]`

## Step Wizard
- Component spec and tokens: **`.cursor/rules/components/step-wizard.mdc`**
- Used on all three wizard screens: `PageInfoForm`, `PageBuilder`, `AdditionalSettings`

## Wizard footer (`PageLevelMenu`)
- Shared sticky footer on **Step 1–3** — see **`.cursor/rules/components/page-level-menu.mdc`**

## Step 1: Page Information (`PageInfoForm.tsx`)
- **Spacing:** `32px` between `StepWizard` and the “Page Information” block (`pt-[32px]` on the content wrapper); content **left-aligned** in the frame (`justify-start`, same `px-[32px]` as the wizard)
- **No card** around fields: **two-column grid** is `w-full` edge-to-edge within horizontal padding (`grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2`, `gap-x-8 gap-y-5`)
- Row pairing: Form Name | HTML Title; **URL Path** full width (`md:col-span-2`); Support Contact | Support Email; Freeze Date (single cell in last row)
- Header: title + single subtitle line (`text-[#7e7e7e]`)
- All inputs use `TextField` (floating-label, 56px, `rounded-[4px]`); wrap each field in `min-w-0` for grid overflow
- Actions: **`PageLevelMenu`** — Cancel + Continue to Page Builder (`primaryDisabled` until required fields valid); no Clear all
- Cover Image has moved to Step 2

## Step 2: Page Builder
- Three-panel: Palette `w-[280px]` | Canvas `flex-1` | Properties `w-[320px]`
- **Palette**: categorised draggable components (Display, Layout, Input, Choices, Date, Pricing, Verification, Address, eCommerce, Other)
- **Display** includes Cover Image (drag-and-drop upload, PNG/JPG up to 5MB)
- **Canvas**: `bg-[#fafafa]`, drop zone `border-[#004299] bg-[#f5f9fe]`, selected `border-[#004299]`
- Input previews: `h-[56px] border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[4px]` floating-label style
- **Properties**: Label, Placeholder, Required/Show toggles, Options list, Validation
- **Bottom bar**: `PageLevelMenu` — includes **Clear all** (canvas) + Back to Page Info + Save & Continue; see `components/page-level-menu.mdc`
- HTML5 Drag and Drop (no external dependency)

## Step 3: Additional Settings
- Primary tabs: Post Transaction | Notifications
- Post Transaction: Redirect URL, Success Message
- Notifications: SMS toggle + text, Email toggle + subject + body
- **Footer**: `PageLevelMenu` with `primaryEmphasis="success"` — Back to Builder + Save & Publish (`bg-[#21c179]`); no Clear all
